# 📚 StudyAI – AI Powered Study Dashboard

StudyAI is a modern web application designed to help students manage their studies efficiently. It combines task management, revision tracking, and AI-powered assistance to improve productivity and learning.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 🔐 Authentication
- User Signup & Login using Firebase Authentication
- Protected routes (only logged-in users can access dashboard)

### 📊 Dashboard
- Overview of study progress
- Task statistics (Completed, Pending, Overdue)
- Visual charts (Bar, Pie, Line)
- Motivational quotes (AI-powered)

### ✅ Task Management
- Add new tasks
- Mark tasks as completed
- Delete tasks
- Tasks stored in Firebase Firestore (user-specific)

### 🔁 Revision Tracker
- Track upcoming revisions
- Identify overdue revision tasks

### 🤖 AI Tools
- AI-powered study assistance using Anthropic API
- Generate study-related responses and motivation

### 🎨 UI/UX
- Clean and modern UI
- Responsive design
- Smooth animations using Framer Motion

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React.js
- React Router DOM
- Framer Motion
- React Icons

### Backend / Services
- Firebase Authentication
- Firebase Firestore (Database)

### AI Integration
- Anthropic Claude API

---

## 📂 Project Structure
src/
│
├── components/ # Reusable UI components
├── pages/ # Main pages (Dashboard, Login, Signup, etc.)
├── services/ # Firebase & AI API services
├── context/ # Global state management
├── hooks/ # Custom React hooks
├── utils/ # Helper functions
│
├── App.jsx # Main app routing
└── main.jsx # Entry point

